defaultThe professional development of school leaders should include school visits and exchan
defaultges with successful schools in working class communities, including to schools in white working class communities. Often communities may be 
defaultsimply
default groups of residents because communities have fractured. In these circumstances the school’s efforts will be about helping to try to turn that group of residents into a community. 
