defaultdefault&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultSuch visits should be both proactive and interactive.  Potential leaders s
defaulthould be expected to explore with school communities the reasons for school success.
